name: The stars, the sea and you
description: #001 of Ether Horizon, the Astrophotography collection. This photo was taken on Milos island, on a beautiful night, when I was alone on the beach. My friends were back at the hotel, drinking on the rooftop, and I still had my feet on the water and the tripod stuck in the sand. I joined them later, and we drank plenty of ouzo to finish off the night.
